Paper: hep-th/9610073

Date: 1996-10-10

Title: Park--Tarter Matrix for a Dyon--Dyon System

Authors: L.G. Mardoyan, A.N. Sissakian, V.M. Ter-Antonyan

Comments: 9 pages, LaTeX file

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A12 (1997) 237-242

The problem of separation of variables in a dyon--dyon system is discussed. Alinear transformation is obtained between fundamental bases of this system.Comparison of the dyon--dyon system with a 4D isotropic oscillator is carriedout.